{"tid":871322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食錯嘢致器官衰竭　入院兩日昏迷　 優質的士司機　求肝續命","createTime":"2018-10-22T00:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T11:15:54.000Z","uid":81228,"like":14,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"36e24682c9491f3bce6fa7ffeb1732a2bd291f9b","tid":871322,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:08:09.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】曾獲選為優質的士司機的周志輝，約一星期前因持續感到不適及疲累求醫，不料經化驗後確診急性肝衰竭，需要換肝續命。然而其妻女的身體狀況均不佳，欲救無從，輝哥女兒阿瑩只望有奇蹟出現，「需要一位好心人的肝臟，希望換到肝救到爸爸！」<br />\n<br />\n記者：翁鈺輝<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181020/large/a0901a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181020%2Flarge%2Fa0901a.jpg&h=b384023e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周志輝一向健康，但不幸患上肝衰竭。 家人提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n現年54歲的輝哥入院後出現肝衰竭，病情急速惡化，需利用呼吸機協助呼吸，急需換肝續命。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>妻女不適宜捐肝</strong><br />\n<br />\n輝哥屬於A型血，院方評估之後認為最好於一星期內接受肝臟移植。望着昏迷卧床的丈夫，輝嫂只能一直陪伴在側，她指丈夫約一星期前因覺得身體不適及「好攰」求醫私家醫生，豈料數日後的化驗報告指其肝酵素指數很高，遂於本周三（17日）到瑪麗醫院求醫，當時輝哥仍「識行識走」。<br />\n<br />\n豈料入院兩天以來，輝哥由清醒變昏迷，至前晚更要用呼吸機協助呼吸，需轉到深切治療部，診斷懷疑輝哥「食錯嘢」感染肝炎引發急性肝衰竭。<br />\n<br />\n輝哥妻子及女兒阿瑩本想捐肝，但兩人因患病及高血壓而未能成事，其他親屬正驗血檢查，但么子輝哥的8位兄姊大都60歲或以上，超過一般適宜捐肝年齡，機會十分渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n輝嫂表示，丈夫偶然會在朋友聚會時小酌減壓，但是健康一直未有大問題，未料病魔猛然來襲。仍在學的阿瑩稱，爸爸每天大清早開工前都會「拉筋」，放工後有時間亦會跑步半至一小時。她指爸爸熱心助人，駕車時必會提醒乘客從安全的一邊門下車，有時見到窮伯伯拾荒又會給對方數十元充飢。<br />\n<br />\n不過這一切俱往矣，這次變成爸爸需要幫助，阿瑩呼籲市民考慮捐活肝或屍肝：「爸爸因肝衰竭陷入昏迷情況十分危殆，需要一位好心人的肝臟，希望換到肝救到爸爸！」兩母女現時盼望奇蹟出現，市民如欲查詢捐肝事宜，可致電瑪麗醫院熱線 2255 3838。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181020/20526509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181020%2F20526509&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0696c2b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181020%2F20526509&h=5bb91275\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181020/20526509</a>"},{"pid":"3d892b14a106501e7b5d74a0c29a5affa06eb81a","tid":871322,"uid":53062,"like":110,"dislike":6,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"食野生靈芝？"},{"pid":"a5cc0c53b7aae8078aed6aa7f6414c0dcd5f5746","tid":871322,"uid":8572,"like":224,"dislike":46,"score":178,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:12:07.000Z","msg":"打風有無濫收車資<br />\n<br />\n平時有無找毫子<br />\n<br />\n有無試過拒載 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中一樣就唔好叫優質 叫陰質的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e121af598d29b3066a488eae529628e6f1c68025","tid":871322,"uid":113000,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:14:08.000Z","msg":"食錯咩<br />\n又食菇?"},{"pid":"601ecc5b8684c002e88f7bd9f714b833f03af7a9","tid":871322,"uid":35014,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4a48395acc93ac680354e3298b7b5449a0805b7","tid":871322,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc1f3031f2d1aebcf7d25865a4bb92f80d1e827","tid":871322,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:16:24.000Z","msg":"其實都幾日之前&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"7d533f13a68446b7e3b6654517c4462283079799","tid":871322,"uid":93078,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"601ecc5b8684c002e88f7bd9f714b833f03af7a9","tid":871322,"uid":35014,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:17:32.000Z","msg":"可能無辦法下 應該得 如果真係冇"},{"pid":"89cc315ee7c50c0a0a94fb3872b99247d6822075","tid":871322,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:19:19.000Z","msg":"有得終身免費坐的士就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb276d2aa2cbebc0735ddd1be7b331d6954f086","tid":871322,"uid":32722,"like":79,"dislike":3,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"89cc315ee7c50c0a0a94fb3872b99247d6822075","tid":871322,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:19:19.000Z","msg":"有得終身免費坐的士就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:21:20.000Z","msg":"以佢人品可能真係有機會<br />\n不過連登仔肯去驗血先算啦，仲講捐器官笑撚死人"},{"pid":"4d4236a73c14fc587d71b66bde7bc86086595e12","tid":871322,"uid":134864,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:22:43.000Z","msg":"係咪食左淡水魚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df25d0d5946faadd2ec1fa96dd55e24859e9092","tid":871322,"uid":95,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:24:38.000Z","msg":"食咩食到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea4fe79e8717c274dfc80418a1444d8a82a72a2","tid":871322,"uid":65328,"like":51,"dislike":4,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:25:11.000Z","msg":"我想知食錯咩野，無理由自己戇鳩要人免費送肝俾你"},{"pid":"ee4bc6b6d19318688d106f0021ef2a0613f8a87e","tid":871322,"uid":58358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4d4236a73c14fc587d71b66bde7bc86086595e12","tid":871322,"uid":134864,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:22:43.000Z","msg":"係咪食左淡水魚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:26:46.000Z","msg":"三文魚（紅鱒）"},{"pid":"07cf4418011cba87724ec959ff424a81c2961bcf","tid":871322,"uid":58358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:30:38.000Z","msg":"甲型肝炎是一種急性病毒性肝炎，通過糞口途徑傳播。進食不清潔的食物和食水，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尤其是未經煮熟的海鮮</span>，很容易感染甲肝病毒。患上急性甲肝的小童一般無明顯症狀，需要驗血才能發現染病。而成年人在發病初期則會較易疲倦及胃口變差，隨著病情惡化，患者可能會出現黃疸（皮膚和眼睛呈現黃色）、尿液變深、嘔心嘔吐、上消化道不適及疲倦等症狀，亦有些患者在發病期間會發燒。<br />\n<br />\n如出現上述急性肝炎症狀，應馬上求醫。醫生會先為病人進行肝功能測試（驗血），急性肝炎患者的谷丙轉氨酶（ALT）會急劇上升，但要確診患上的是甲肝而不是其他肝炎，還須測試甲肝病毒血清抗體（IgM anti-HAV），結果呈陽性即表示所患的是急性甲肝。<br />\n<br />\n要預防感染甲肝，關鍵是注意飲食衛生。在發病期間，患者雖然可以和他人一起進餐，但必須勤於洗手，排泄後亦應盡快洗刷廁所。到較落後的國家旅行時，選擇一些衛生設施完善的地方進餐，並應確保食物完全煮熟才可進食。現在雖已有一些有效的甲肝疫苗，但這些疫苗要在分兩次注射，中間事隔 6 至 8 個月才會有效。<br />\n<br />\n若病人在甲型肝炎抗體IgG 抗HAV（IgG anti-HAV）免疫球蛋白測試中呈陽性反應，即表示病人曾感染甲肝並擁有免疫能力。雖然這個測試並非必要，但有些醫生會在注射甲肝疫苗前，為病人先檢查IgG抗HAV免疫球蛋白。<br />\n<br />\n當患者出現甲肝症狀後，傳染性就會明顯下降，但甲肝病毒的潛伏期可達兩個月，因此在發病前患者可能已把病毒傳染給他人。如懷疑被甲肝病毒感染的話，可以注射免疫球蛋白以作預防。"},{"pid":"424434bc07f3d5a5ae134f7231739c2ba3e6613a","tid":871322,"uid":69924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3cb276d2aa2cbebc0735ddd1be7b331d6954f086","tid":871322,"uid":32722,"like":79,"dislike":3,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"89cc315ee7c50c0a0a94fb3872b99247d6822075","tid":871322,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:19:19.000Z","msg":"有得終身免費坐的士就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:21:20.000Z","msg":"以佢人品可能真係有機會<br />\n不過連登仔肯去驗血先算啦，仲講捐器官笑撚死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:32:54.000Z","msg":"捐肝好多保險唔保"},{"pid":"d3fce334de957e4558f5695e49003ae29130548c","tid":871322,"uid":205254,"like":82,"dislike":68,"score":14,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:45:39.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好撚仆街 見人出事唔係去關心人先 反而係去質疑人係咪陰質司機 已經唔奢望你去捐肝救人 簡單一句鼓勵留言都無  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd94edfe631113dcdebdd3e3609cf180c02adfd3","tid":871322,"uid":20241,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:31:13.000Z","msg":"輝哥妻子及女兒阿瑩本想捐肝，但兩人因患病及高血壓而未能成事，其他親屬正驗血檢查，但么子輝哥的8位兄姊大都60歲或以上，超過一般適宜捐肝年齡，機會十分渺茫<br />\n<br />\n妻女：損肝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e334cf94252